  "prompt": "Which is a good inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Coffee County AL?",
  "response": "Finding the right inpatient drug and alcohol rehabilitation center is a crucial step toward recovery. Near Coffee County, Alabama, there are several reputable facilities you might consider:\n\n### 1. **Southern State Hospital \u2013 Dothan Campus**\n- **Location:** Dothan, AL\n- **Services:** Offers comprehensive inpatient treatment programs for substance abuse, including detoxification, individual and group therapy, and aftercare planning.\n- **Contact:** (334) 432-8210\n- **Website:** [Southern State Hospital Dothan](https://www.alabamamedicaid.gov/providers/covered-services/southern-state-hospital)\n\n### 2. **Bursley Hospital**\n- **Location:** Dothan, AL\n- **Services:** Specializes in mental health and substance abuse treatment with inpatient programs tailored to individual needs.\n- **Contact:** (334) 263-4200\n- **Website:** [Bursley Hospital](https://www.bursleyhospital.org/)\n\n### 3. **Coastal Recovery Centers**\n- **Location:** Dothan, AL\n- **Services:** Provides inpatient rehabilitation with a focus on personalized treatment plans, including therapy, counseling, and support groups.\n- **Contact:** (334) 485-4875\n- **Website:** [Coastal Recovery Centers](https://www.coastalrecoverycenters.com/)\n\n### 4. **Regions Behavioral Health**\n- **Location:** Dothan, AL\n- **Services:** Offers a range of inpatient services for substance abuse, including medical detox, psychiatric services, and comprehensive therapy programs.\n- **Contact:** (334) 262-8500\n- **Website:** [Regions Behavioral Health](https://www.regionsbh.org/)\n\n### 5. **Elba Residential Treatment Center**\n- **Location:** Elba, AL (if available)\n- **Services:** [If a local facility is available, provide details here. If not, consider noting that nearby facilities are in Dothan.]\n\n### Additional Resources:\n- **Alabama Department of Mental Health:** They can provide information and referrals to licensed treatment facilities in your area.\n  - **Website:** [Alabama DMH](https://dsmh.alabama.gov/)\n  - **Helpline:** 1-800-282-2221\n\n### Tips for Choosing a Rehab Center:\n1. **Assess Services Offered:** Ensure the facility provides comprehensive care, including medical detox, therapy, and aftercare planning.\n2. **Check Accreditation:** Look for centers accredited by reputable organizations like the Joint Commission or CARF.\n3. **Consider Location:** Proximity to family and support systems can be beneficial for recovery.\n4. **Review Costs and Insurance:** Verify if the center accepts your insurance or offers payment plans.\n5. **Visit the Facility:** If possible, tour the facility to get a sense of the environment and staff.\n\n**Important:** It's essential to consult with a healthcare professional or a counselor to determine the best treatment plan for your specific needs. Early intervention can significantly improve the chances of a successful recovery.",
